::Magmatron::
    
    "Bazooka bring Bobertron back to base, put him in the CR chamber." 
Magmatron yelled.

______________________________________________________________________
::Bazooka::

    "Understood." He yelled back to Magmatron. He started to drag Bobertron 
back to base. He reached the entrance and the autoguns locked onto Bobertron. 
"Autoguns offline" Bazooka said. Once he got Bobertron to the CR chamber he 
turned the Autoguns back on.
